Syntax: gold

Displays the exact amount of gold you are currently carrying. The game
uses a single currency (gold coins). Gold is used to buy items from shops,
pay for healing at temples, and is received from selling items, sacrificing
objects, and killing monsters.

A quick summary of ways to gain gold:
  - Kill monsters and loot their corpses (get all corpse / loot)
  - Sell unwanted items to shopkeepers (list, value, sell)
  - Sacrifice items at a temple (sacrifice <item>)
  - Receive gold from other players (split, give)

See also: worth score split give sacrifice
